p A Behavior is an Action (an intercardinal point on the #{link_to 'Bipolar Cycle', bipolar_path}) in a specific Realm: #{link_to_or Realm.linear}.
p A Symptom is an excessive, compulsive, obsessive, unhealthy, or unbalancing Behavior. A Behavior which is so bad for you or those around you that you take or are given drugs so that you will <em>stop doing it</em>.

